## The bill object

> Sample Response

```json
{
  "balance": 100,
  "dueDate": "<%= config.futureDate %>",
  "status": "upcoming", 
  "settings": {
    "autoPay": true 
  }
}
```

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`balance` | Current bill balance.
`dueDate` | Current bill due date.
`status` | Status of the bill. Possible values are `paid`, `pending`, `upcoming`, `overdue`, `syncing`.
`settings` | Settings for a bill.
`settings.autopay` | Whether or not this bill is to be paid automatically.